    "Choosing the right lessons in the early years can improve the research process.",
    "In this combined method, the N-gram query classification and the ontology are used to retrieve useful information and make an accurate recommendation.",
    "Generally, the query is converted to N-gram in the preprocessing step.",
    "The query extension is then applied using WordNet to retrieve similar words.",
    "They are then retrieved, and duplicate lessons are removed."
